data.text: @FedGamer I did thanks! :) I also like it that you always send me recognizable landmarks, being the filthy Northern scum that I am - thinking London is just Tower Bridge, Shard, Parliment, and that Bridge we see on the CentralTV logo ;)
@moobit Haha I don't even remember where that was! But when I saw it on my gift list I thought you'd appreciate it 😄
